description._content: Catalog #: 09_01914 Title: Brigadier General Clarence S. ""Bill"" Irvine Special Collection Photo Additional Information: Clarence S. Irvine exiting a navy aircraft, being greeted by unidentified man in military uniform. March 1959, Brigadier General Clarence Irvine enjoyed a long distinguished military career, mainly involving engineering. He served with the XXI Bomber Command (B-29's) during WWII and continued to serve throughout the 1950s and 1960s. Tags: Brigadier General Clarence S.
